      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index is the primary regulatory acceptance criterion. WSS and scalar dissipation rate are mechanistically linked to red blood cell damage and are used to compute RH via the power-law hemolysis model. QoI relevance is fully established. Required level 2 is met."
