      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used for validation must be representative of the COU device geometry and lot-to-lot variability must be characterized.",
      "rationale": "Three pump units from the same manufacturing lot were used in the FDA experimental campaign. Dimensional inspection confirms geometric conformance to nominal within ±0.08 mm. Inter-unit variability in measured RH is 4.1%, which is within the stated experimental uncertainty. Required level 2 is met."
