      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters must be demonstrably equivalent to those used in the validation experiments, or differences must be bounded by sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "A one-at-a-time sensitivity analysis was performed for viscosity (±5%), rotational speed (±50 RPM), and inlet flow rate (±0.2 L/min). Maximum sensitivity of RH to these perturbations is 3.8%, confirming that parameter equivalency is maintained within the validation uncertainty budget. Required level 2 is met."
