    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 3. The Use error factor is recorded as not-assessed based on the team's judgment that automated post-processing pipelines eliminate operator-induced error pathways. The overall credibility assessment is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model adequately predicts worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device, with the relative hemolysis index remaining below 1.0 relative to the predicate device across all five evaluated operating points.",
